{"tid":597472,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"又開火！雲高爾責曼聯球星唔睇email","createTime":"2018-03-18T16:12:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-19T04:38:53.000Z","uid":122,"like":11,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"924bbcfcff0a3cb75dd619c4d3531df76b0342fc","tid":597472,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T16:12:29.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=Pvww11BRZGe2XT2%2BG%2FNVY0%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=61455d3f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】前拜仁慕尼黑和曼聯主帥雲高爾，日前接受訪問時指出曼聯球星很不專業，不願意閱讀電子郵件。<br />\n<br />\n前拜仁慕尼黑和曼聯主帥雲高爾（Louis van Gaal），日前接受德國《圖片報》訪問，提及過往在紅魔執教時所發生的事情，更揚言當年需要教導曼聯球星閱讀電子郵件。<br />\n<br />\n「這是真的。我發送郵件至所有球員，在內容中指出，例如是他們的優點和缺點。我與IT人員一起建立了追踪器，追踪所有郵件，看看哪些球員打開了，並確保他們可以順利打開。此舉的目的是希望所有人在家內會面，又或是視像與我會面對話時，能夠有好一點的準備。可是此舉卻發現了他們的不專業，需要我向他們作出糾正。」<br />\n<br />\n雲高爾其後續說：「但我在拜仁執教時已使用電子郵件的方法，我的信念是一名完整的專業人士，也希望以專業的方式生活。正如洛賓一樣，他就有閱讀電子郵件。」<br />\n<br />\n另外雲高爾亦提及執教曼聯時，希望從拜仁簽入前鋒羅拔利雲度夫斯基，「他是目前世上其中一位最佳前鋒。我亦希望執教利雲度夫斯基，帶他到曼聯，價錢方面對紅魔來說不是問題，但拜仁卻不願意讓他離隊。」"},{"pid":"a685eb5c84697edc585064a5a98f30301ff33435","tid":597472,"uid":164590,"like":38,"dislike":10,"score":28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T16:16:35.000Z","msg":"狗點識睇字"},{"pid":"b285bb0c77ee79205512c00551b7b18062d2b306","tid":597472,"uid":94771,"like":32,"dislike":8,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T16:21:13.000Z","msg":"雖然唔鍾意獌<br />\n但雲高爾真係好撚怨婦<br />\n不個都幾期待條友有得報復"},{"pid":"6a31019e50314760a9978b33246b212c4c6a7784","tid":597472,"uid":165817,"like":13,"dislike":3,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"b285bb0c77ee79205512c00551b7b18062d2b306","tid":597472,"uid":94771,"like":32,"dislike":8,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T16:21:13.000Z","msg":"雖然唔鍾意獌<br />\n但雲高爾真係好撚怨婦<br />\n不個都幾期待條友有得報復"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T16:29:04.000Z","msg":"記者唔問佢都唔會特別講返啦<br />\n你估佢真係咁痴線咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0463a830ffb27f68b9bd3b11e54206a3b42eeea9","tid":597472,"uid":71393,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T16:30:04.000Z","msg":"屌, 開EMAIL咪睇佢D 死亡筆記<br />\n比我都唔睇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41ac687cd3130cfbefb3caa45fd3e1ae83cbe5df","tid":597472,"uid":71393,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T16:32:05.000Z","msg":"v92 咁樣教獌真係有d危"},{"pid":"090dce4cf10c3d737241fab703e905571932c9ab","tid":597472,"uid":55644,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T16:38:13.000Z","msg":"垃圾領隊<br />\n講野當面講啦<br />\n用email做乜尻"},{"pid":"77c97c5ec99b77591c6810cca4edcfcec6f5fbb6","tid":597472,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T16:56:58.000Z","msg":"敢帥是無辜的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec4f77d19024b4547c6df8718e5d1a08926b1fae","tid":597472,"uid":22229,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T16:59:20.000Z","msg":"同肥賓比usb c朗睇簡直異曲同弓"},{"pid":"256b4f72a548a35abea90335658a38295066fb4c","tid":597472,"uid":12034,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"090dce4cf10c3d737241fab703e905571932c9ab","tid":597472,"uid":55644,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T16:38:13.000Z","msg":"垃圾領隊<br />\n講野當面講啦<br />\n用email做乜尻"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T17:00:59.000Z","msg":"ok屌你老母"},{"pid":"24439359f5caf2a9a817c3b7c3b5905377be2706","tid":597472,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T17:06:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#b"},{"pid":"a0311bc06f789b48839154049403a0c7811eae71","tid":597472,"uid":712,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T17:10:54.000Z","msg":"問心 打工仔收左工仲會唔會睇老細email先"},{"pid":"b4df4286ffe48bf47eec2e29b3980a9de1adb60a","tid":597472,"uid":31611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"